description: Recently sold: $240,000. Sharp, clean multi level home situated on 5 acres & set up for hobby farm. Heated & insulated 24x32 workshop, 24x44 pole building plus 18x24 concrete stable w/4 tie stalls and fenced pasture. 4 bedroom home is spotless! Vaulted main level living room w/corner gas fireplace and tons of natural light. Spacious sun room includes hot tub & tiered deck w/pergola. Natural gas, close to schools - 45 minutes to Cambridge!

Recently sold: $169,900. Investment opportunity! Additional pole barn for all the extra toys and storage. House needs many cosmetic repairs but structure seems good. Close to town, but out far enough for privacy. Great potential to be a great house once again. Sold as-is. Septic is compliant.
